QuestData.Title: Dark Enemies
QuestData.Description: Your arrival should be cause for celebration, hero, but I fear our troubles are just beginning.$B$BWarlord Ner'zhul and his Shadowmoon clan have launched a surprise attack on a draenei settlement to the north.$B$BProphet Velen has gone to aid the wounded at Teluuna Observatory, but we need more defenders.$B$BI must go to assist the others. If you wish to help us, go to Arbor Glen and kill any Shadowmoon enemies that you see.
QuestData.RewardText: The forests are clear of Shadowmoon enemies? Good. I knew that you would not fail.
